trans-unit.source: Contains a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção somente leitura de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> controles.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class contains the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> controls that exist on a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartZoneCollection contém a coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>controles que existem em uma página de Web Parts.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: It is used primarily by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control to track and manage all the zones.
trans-unit.target: Ele é usado principalmente pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle para controlar e gerenciar todas as zonas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control keeps a reference to the collection of zones on a page in its read-only <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle mantém uma referência para o conjunto de zonas em uma página em seu somente leitura <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class is useful when you want to carry out operations on multiple zones or their contents at the same time, or when you need to locate a particular zone and examine or change its contents.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartZoneCollection é útil quando você quiser executar operações em várias zonas ou seu conteúdo ao mesmo tempo, ou quando você precisa localizar uma zona específica e examinar ou alterar seu conteúdo.

trans-unit.source: Although the collection of zones itself is read-only and you cannot change the size of the collection object itself, you can still get references to the individual zones within the collection, and when you have a reference to an individual zone object, you can change its property values.
trans-unit.target: Embora o conjunto de zonas em si é somente leitura e não é possível alterar o tamanho do objeto da coleção em si, você ainda pode obter referências para as regiões individuais dentro da coleção e quando você tem uma referência a um objeto de zona individual, você pode alterar seus valores de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class has two constructors.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartZoneCollection tem dois construtores.

trans-unit.source: The first one, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>, simply initializes an empty instance of a new WebPartZoneCollection.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro deles, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>, simplesmente inicializa uma instância vazia de um novo WebPartZoneCollection.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>

trans-unit.source: The second one, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>, initializes a collection by passing in an existing collection of zones.
trans-unit.target: O outro, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>, inicializa uma coleção, passando uma coleção existente de zonas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class contains an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartZoneCollection contém um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property allows you to locate a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> control within the collection by passing in a string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade permite que você localize um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>controle dentro da coleção, passando um identificador de cadeia de caracteres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The zone is located by matching the string identifier to the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> property on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: A zona está localizada por meio da correspondência de identificador de cadeia de caracteres para o valor da <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>propriedade em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>zona.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class also has several methods that are useful for examining or accessing its contents.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartZoneCollection também tem vários métodos que são úteis para examinar ou acessar seu conteúdo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A> method determines whether a particular zone exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A>método determina se uma determinada região existe na coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A> method copies the collection to an array of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A>método copia a coleção para uma matriz de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>objetos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A> method returns the index of a particular zone within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Por fim, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A>método retorna o índice de uma zona específica na coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma instância vazia do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses this constructor within its own constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> class for a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle usa este construtor dentro de seu próprio construtor para inicializar uma nova instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>classe para uma página de Web Parts.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"></xref> class by passing in a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"> </xref> classe, passando uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Use the WebPartZoneCollection constructor when you want to create a custom collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> objects to carry out programmatic operations on them.
trans-unit.target: Use o construtor de WebPartZoneCollection quando você deseja criar uma coleção personalizada do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objetos para executar operações programáticas neles.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: For example, you could access the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> property and create a subset of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> objects on a Web Parts page, assigning them to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> object, and then carry out operations on the child controls or various properties of only that subset of zones.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, você poderá acessar o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>propriedade e criar um subconjunto de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objetos em uma página de Web Parts, atribuindo-os para uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>de objeto e, em seguida, executar operações em controles filho ou várias propriedades de apenas esse subconjunto de regiões.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> objetos.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The collection of zones is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: É o conjunto de zonas <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: One of the objects in the collection is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or is not of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um dos objetos na coleção é <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> ou não é do tipo <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular zone exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se uma determinada região existe na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object and determine whether it is in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: O método contém permite que você verifique se um determinado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>do objeto e determinar se ele está em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> que é verificada para determinar se ele está na coleção.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular zone is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um valor booliano que indica se uma determinada região está na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Copia a coleção para uma matriz de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to create a custom array that can contain the zones in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection, a subset of those zones, or a superset of those zones.
trans-unit.target: O método CopyTo é útil quando você deseja criar um conjunto personalizado que pode conter as zonas no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>coleção, um subconjunto dessas zonas, ou um subconjunto dessas zonas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> array to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> matriz contém a coleção copiada.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: O ponto de partida na matriz na qual colocar o conteúdo da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a posição de um membro específico da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zones on a Web Parts page, and you need to know the ordinal position of one zone relative to the other zones.
trans-unit.target: O método IndexOf será útil se você tiver vários <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>zonas em uma página de Web Parts e você precisam saber a posição ordinal de uma zona em relação a outras zonas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> que é um membro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um inteiro que indica a posição de um objeto específico da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specific member of the collection by passing in an integer.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um membro específico da coleção, passando um inteiro.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection by using an index number that represents its ordinal position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade de Item permite que você acesse um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objeto dentro de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>coleção usando um número de índice que representa a posição ordinal na coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The index number for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> within a collection.
trans-unit.target: O número de índice para um determinado <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> dentro de uma coleção.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> no índice especificado na coleção.

trans-unit.target: Correspondência de todos os identificadores de cadeia de caracteres diferencia maiusculas de minúsculas.
